GOTTSCHALL
v.
CRANE. No. S222887. Supreme Court of California July 13, 2016.

CANTIL-SAKAUYE, C.J., WERDEGAR, CHIN, CORRIGAN, LIU, CUÉLLAR, and KRUGER, JJ., concur.

Dismissed and remanded to CA 1/2. In light of the decision in Webb v. Special Electric Co. (2016) 63 Cal.4th 167, 202 Cal.Rptr.3d 460, 370 P.3d 1022, review in this matter is dismissed.
